{
  "stem": "10699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So after that, we didn't have any-- only, only, only, only trenches we did after that till we were on the-- on the new-- on the other selection, a big selection.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you mustn't forget, every time when there was a selection, when you went through, Mengele was-- most of the time was there, you never knew if it was your last day.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some girls, you know, tried to pinch their cheeks, you know, they should look rosy, or they shouldn't get too thin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you couldn't help it, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With the diet you were on and the work you worked, you weren't supposed to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you, you gradually went down, down, down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There we were-- we were selected again here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know what we were selected for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were selected in that convoy of a thousand girls that went to Bergen-Belsen on the 31st of October.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By then, we didn't look a pretty sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were put in a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how many days we travelled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We arrived in Bergen-Belsen in a terrible state.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just spoke to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was in the same convoy because the dates are exactly the same.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we arrived there, they put us in tents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had no proper barracks for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was a terrible storm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the barracks collapsed-- the tents collapsed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they fell onto us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we were put somewhere where we were in the open.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I recently asked-- and now-- Janine, my sister-in-law, and other people, I said, I cannot remember that we got food in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can you remember if we got food?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said only sometimes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In Bergen-Belsen, actually, they put us in the tent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- after, you know, we traveled in these trucks on straw, dirty, no food, no, no, no, no hygiene, no nothing-- for the flies, I suppose, already.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were lying-- we couldn't even lie like sardines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to lay like squashed sardines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Therefore, a girl that was sleeping like a sardine and with her legs on my tummy scratched me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that scratch became an anthrax [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] because, there-- you know, there were dirty feet and dirty nails.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to this day, I feel it, because eventually, they put in-- they didn't have much, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became an anthrax.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So without anesthetic or anything, she, she pierced it, put some kind of gauze in it with a disinfectant, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but there was nobody to look after it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because after that-- that was-- must have been quite a time later, because when they took it out, there was now maggots in it, full of maggots, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just maggots that had grown in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that left me with a scar that I can even today tell the change of weather.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the conditions in Bergen-Belsen were just that you were here to die, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in barracks, except for being-- go for Appell, being beaten up for no reason whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Food I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on one Appell on the 1st of January-- because I will never forget it because I knew it was the 1st of January-- they made a general Appell-- 'Appell,' it means 'call-up' in Bergen-Belsen-- where everybody had to come out in the open and stand.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sick, the old, the-- everybody had to come out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to stand there 12 hours in the snow and ice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just wanted to watch how many will die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And a few of us came out of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that was the 1st of January, '45, yeah?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
